    "[Information] Each user i can read the messages produced by the set N r i (t) of accounts they have subscribed to and eventually share them with their own subscribers N d i (t).",
    "3.2 Subscription networks between users of a social networking site can be represented by an evolving directed network",
    "in which an edge s ij exists when the user j has suscribed to i's account (information flows from i to j)."
